    "Scanning…" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "スキャン中…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Send Test OSD" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "テスト OSD を送信"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Sends the current iPhone time to the goggle OSD. Each press shows a different value, so it's obvious when packets land." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "現在の iPhone の時刻をゴーグルの OSD に送信します。押すたびに値が変わるため、パケットが届いているかひと目でわかります。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Settings" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "設定"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Start TX UID Capture" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "TX UID キャプチャを開始"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Stop" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "停止"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Switching pairing… waiting for goggle to settle." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "ペアリングを切り替え中… ゴーグルの安定を待機中。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Target lap" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "目標ラップ数"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Target pace" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "目標ペース"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Target pace is race time ÷ (target lap − 1)." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "目標ペース = レース時間 ÷ (目標ラップ数 − 1)。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This switches the M5Stick to a fresh pairing ID and broadcasts it to your goggle in one step.\n\nMake sure your goggle is in bind mode (ELRS menu → Bind) BEFORE tapping Apply, otherwise the goggle won't pick up the new pairing.\n\nIf your goggle's backpack was flashed with a fixed bind phrase, the goggle will silently revert to that on its next reboot — use Restore previous goggle to get lap times back.\n\nCurrent pairing: %@" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "M5Stick を新しいペアリング ID に切り替え、その ID を一度の操作でゴーグルへブロードキャストします。\n\n「適用」をタップする前に、ゴーグルがバインドモード(ELRS メニュー → Bind)になっていることを必ず確認してください。そうしないと、ゴーグルは新しいペアリングを受け取りません。\n\nゴーグルのバックパックが固定のバインドフレーズで書き込まれている場合、再起動後は静かにそのフレーズへ戻ります — その場合は「前のゴーグルに戻す」でラップタイムを復帰できます。\n\n現在のペアリング: %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "TX UID Capture" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "TX UID キャプチャ"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "UID: %@" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "UID: %@"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Unknown" : {
      "comment" : "Fallback name for an unidentified BLE peripheral.",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "不明"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "unknown" : {
      "comment" : "Inline placeholder for the From/To/Current pairing UID inside the apply-confirmation alert.",
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "不明"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Use Bind Phrase mode with the same phrase that was flashed, or reflash the backpack with the new phrase." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "書き込み済みと同じフレーズで「バインドフレーズ」モードを使用するか、新しいフレーズでバックパックを再書き込みしてください。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Verifying lap times can reach the goggle…" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "ja" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
